author: Brandon Wenerd
title: This Is The Greatest Story Ever About Walking In Late To A College Lecture
text:
We’ve all been there — You have an aggressive night of drinking bottom-shelf tequila on a Tuesday night and you forget you have a big college lecture to go to in the morning. You show up 15 minutes late and every seat is taken. 
That’s when an experience like the following goes down. Georgia State University’s @yalljust_myfans captured this ridiculous story last week, as told on Now That’s College .
